{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Give legal gender recognition to non-binary+ people",
        "additional_details": "I myself as a nonbinary individual who is on the spectrum understand the difficulties that nonbinary+ and neurodivergent people face. It has angered me that we do not have these rights, and I think that it is time to change. It would help countless people, and you can help by signing this petition.",
        "background": "What I want the Government/Parliament to do:\r\n - For nonbinary+ people to have Legal Gender Recognition (for people to be able to put N/A or none of the above or X etc on legal documents)\r\n- Marriage/Civil Partnership labels to be other than bride or groom\r\n- Legal gender-neutral titles (such as Mx)",
